summary: A rusty, old and grimly dark Sweetfx ENB preset, A blast from another ancient time long ago forgotten.
descriptionHtml:
[center][size=6][b][i][u]ENB Octavo De

[youtube]ogmQzdkxd50[/youtube]

[/u][/i][/b][size=4][b][i][u]M'tesh[/u][/i][/b] gives you his Eighth attempt at an ENB preset.
M'tesh has wish to go with an old rustic anicent broody outlook.
Simpley compatable with most weather and lighting and water mods, though it might have a different look  on what you use.
Me used C.O.T v5 and Pure Waters.
[/size][size=4]Just drop in your Skyrim folder and set in your Skyrim Prefs bFloatPointRenderTarget =0 to =1
then go to[url=http://enbdev.com/mod_tesskyrim_v0108.html][b]ENBSeries v0.108 TrueHDR[/b][/url] [/size][size=4]and extract the d3d9.dll File from the wrapper and add it to your skyrim folder[/size][b][i][u]

[/u][/i][/b][/size][font=Comic Sans MS][size=5]ENB by Boris Vorotsov
